column2: "Ah,<%me>. What a coincidence."
"I wanted to interact with the Lillipans, thus I asked Fourier for help but...."
"Lilili! Lilili!"
"Hey, its fine... Matoi is part of ARKS, She isn't an enemy."
"Li! Li!"
"I can't help you. I have no idea why is he so wary of you."
"I wonder if I have offended him somehow..."
"I've been with him all this time, so that shouldn't be the case..."
"Li! Lili! Lilili!"
"Hmm... It feels like he isn't angry at you, but stopping you from going further instead."
"Looks like he only has issues with Matoi... Does anyone know why?"
"Mm... Even if you say so... I don't remember doing anything here before..."
"1. It could be something in the past."
"2. No point brooding over it."
"I give up... I can't recall anything."
"Yes, you are right. It could be something I have done in past that I forgot."
"Thanks Fourier. I don't wish to disturb the Lillipans any further. Guess I'll head back now."
"Sorry Matoi, I was not of any help to you."
"Don't say that, inviting this Lillipan here is more than enough."
"All these while, I've only heard stories about them. For me to be able to meet them makes me really happy."
"Let's visit them together again? I am sure he would welcome you the next time we visit."
"Yes, definitely."
